## Exception Tipleri

```python
from app.core.exceptions import AIServiceError, ContentPolicyError

# AIServiceError: API çağrısı başarısız (timeout, HTTP 4xx/5xx, parse hatası)
raise AIServiceError(f"Gemini yanıt hatası: {response.status_code}")

# ContentPolicyError: İçerik politikası ihlali (çocuk güvenliği, uygunsuz içerik)
raise ContentPolicyError("İçerik politikasına aykırı üretim engellendi")
```

## Overlay Uygulama

```python
from PIL import Image

def apply_overlay(base_image: Image.Image, product: Product) -> Image.Image:
    if not product.has_overlay:
        return base_image
    overlay = Image.open(download_from_gcs(product.overlay_url)).convert("RGBA")
    overlay = overlay.resize(base_image.size, Image.LANCZOS)
    if product.overlay_opacity < 1.0:
        alpha = overlay.split()[3]
        alpha = alpha.point(lambda p: int(p * product.overlay_opacity))
        overlay.putalpha(alpha)
    return Image.alpha_composite(base_image.convert("RGBA"), overlay)
```
